1
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:14,959
Hello.

2
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:15,719
Brother.

3
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,400
Lunar.

4
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,599
I thought you

5
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,200
would never talk to me again.

6
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,280
Have you come back?

7
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,159
I'm with Dad.

8
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,840
He has something to tell you.

9
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:32,719
Hello.

10
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:33,719
Lunar.

11
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,719
How are you?

12
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,120
I heard from Chen

13
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:40,159
you're studying the wild wolves.

14
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,319
If you need any help,

15
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,640
just let me know.

16
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,680
What do you want to do?

17
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,280
I just want

18
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,640
our family to have a meal together,

19
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:51,879
and have a chat.

20
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,519
I've been busy lately.

21
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:54,840
Busy?

22
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,519
Then invite more people.

23
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,599
Nowadays, many media

24
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,920
are very interested in extraterrestrial creatures.

25
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,959
Once your friend Wild Wolf

26
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,599
is exposed,

27
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:07,599
it will be a shocking news.

28
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,479
You know what I mean?

29
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:39,360
Are you going out?

30
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:41,680
To meet a friend.

31
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,080
To talk about the observation report.

32
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,039
Then

33
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:48,479
remember not to reveal my identity.

34
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,759
I'm leaving.

35
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:58,199
Bye.

36
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,000
See you tonight.

37
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,479
Hello.

38
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:21,840
Bro.

39
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:22,800
Something happened.

40
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,639
We agreed to have dinner together.

41
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,240
Why did you pick this place?

42
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,719
Moyue.

43
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,199
Dad is

44
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:37,919
getting more and more confused about what you're thinking.

45
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,199
Uncle Xie.

46
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,319
You should

47
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,159
remember this place, right?

48
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,400
Really?

49
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,520
Sixteen years ago,

50
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:51,159
you and my mom Jiang Jie

51
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:54,039
came here to investigate the rumor of Wild Wolf.

52
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:01,120
Don't be fooled by Lu Zhiyu's sweet talk.

53
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,479
We are a family.

54
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:11,439
What if I saw it with my own eyes?

55
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,080
What did you see?

56
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:18,560
Back then,

57
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,720
you drove into this forest,

58
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:24,160
but you didn't know I crawled into the car out of curiosity

59
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,519
and listened to you from the back seat.

60
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,600
Such an important discovery,

61
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,000
and at such a critical moment,

62
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:33,160
how could you let that wolf go?

63
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,439
I'm a scholar,

64
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,639
not a poacher.

65
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,920
If your speculation is true,

66
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,120
we can get his serum

67
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,839
and develop a drug that extends life.

68
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,560
At that time,

69
00:04:43,759 --> 00:04:44,959
you will have wealth and fame,

70
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,959
which you never dared to dream of before.

71
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,839
I won't do anything against scientific ethics,

72
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,279
and I won't allow you to do so.

73
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,160
When your plan was blocked,

74
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,879
you bribed Qin Yeren

75
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,759
to fake a drowning accident

76
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:57,160
to kill

77
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,720
the only witness you thought.

78
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:02,079
You thought you could kill the wolves.

79
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,399
But Lu Zhiyu's appearance

80
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:06,920
saved them

81
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,399
and another witness.

82
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:11,439
Me.

83
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,639
I was too soft

84
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:18,839
to kill you.

85
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,240
Otherwise, there wouldn't have been so many troubles.

86
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,120
Is it because you were too soft,

87
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,120
or you just didn't find the right opportunity?

88
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:28,879
You brought me back to the country,

89
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,279
and you dare not create another murder.

90
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,079
So you had a psychiatrist treat my nightmares,

91
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,360
and implanted those illusions you created.

92
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,879
Xie Qiming,

93
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:43,160
you've controlled me for sixteen years,

94
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,560
do you want to control my entire life?

95
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,439
You know everything.

96
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,199
It doesn't matter.

97
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:56,519
You helped me

98
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:59,120
find the beast again.

99
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:00,439
I bet

100
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:03,120
he's on his way to save you.

101
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,079
Just be my trap.

102
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,600
Wait for him to come into the trap.

103
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,079
Chen.

104
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,560
After this,

105
00:06:22,199 --> 00:06:24,839
you can be with your sister forever.

106
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,759
Lu Zhiyu.

107
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,279
Xiaoya.

108
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,920
Lu Zhiyu, come out.

109
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:32,800
Qin Yeren.

110
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,639
You finally came.

111
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,680
Xiaoya is in a safe place now.

112
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,120
Let's talk about our business.

113
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,839
Go talk to the King of Hell.

114
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,920
Qin Yeren.

115
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,480
You always say you love Xiaoya.

116
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,439
Do you deserve her by doing this?

117
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,040
Cut the crap.

118
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:57,199
You don't deserve a daughter like Xiaoya,

119
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,639
nor do you deserve to be a father.

120
00:06:58,879 --> 00:07:00,000
Go to hell.

121
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:02,720
Dad!

122
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:04,360
Xiaoya!

123
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,319
You're lying!

124
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,839
The evidence is clear as day!

125
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,959
I know everything you've done!

126
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:11,759
Xiaoya,

127
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:14,079
I've arranged a safe place for you.

128
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,279
Go!

129
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,160
Go!

130
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,120
No!

131
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,759
Dad, can you...

132
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:21,160
Can you stop being so stubborn?

133
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:24,279
You worked for them for so many years,

134
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:27,439
but in the end, you lost all your men.

135
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,160
But they,

136
00:07:29,879 --> 00:07:31,360
as you said, are beasts,

137
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,879
they took me in and helped me

138
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,439
when I was at my lowest.

139
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,199
Dad,

140
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,800
I know you were angry with me that day,

141
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:41,920
and you deliberately drove me away,

142
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,680
just to make me cut ties with them.

143
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:47,120
But I'm your daughter,

144
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:50,240
how could I possibly leave you behind?

145
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,720
Xiaoya.

146
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,000
Dad.

147
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,800
I'm sorry, Dad.

148
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,800
I've already called the police.

149
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,199
Xiaoya.

150
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,399
It's all my fault.

151
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,079
Turning yourself in

152
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,439
is the only way for you to survive.

153
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:55,919
My dad used to hold me a lot when I was little.

154
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,480
But when I grew up,

155
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,600
he never held me again.

156
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,360
Xuchen.

157
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:32,879
Let them say goodbye.

158
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:36,639
Run!

159
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:38,519
Lu Zhiyu, run!

160
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,759
He was exposed to a large dose of animal toxin,

161
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,639
which can kill an elephant.

162
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,080
The faster the blood circulates,

163
00:10:46,519 --> 00:10:47,559
the quicker the toxin spreads.

164
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,960
Sixteen years ago,

165
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,879
you ruined my plans.

166
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,639
Today,

167
00:10:58,559 --> 00:10:59,519
Lu Zhiyu,

168
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,879
I'll burn your old nest to ashes.

169
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,519
But don't worry.

170
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:06,960
Your displaced kind

171
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,720
will be taken in by my lab.

172
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,799
You wishful thinking.

173
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:14,240
Do you think everyone is like you,

174
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,840
heartless?

175
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,240
Family

176
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,639
is the least important thing

177
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:26,080
in this world.

178
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:28,639
It will only be a drag.

179
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:30,519
Go.

180
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:36,039
Brother.

181
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,039
Brother.

182
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:45,720
Brother.

183
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,000
Brother.

184
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:50,840
Dad.

185
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:53,320
Please.

186
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,600
Let Moon go.

187
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:02,360
Chen.

188
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,200
Brother.
